An '''advanced bio-stabilizer mask''' analyzed circulation patterns through the skin, monitored breathing through chemical sensors, and reactions through [[Eye/Legends|eye]] movements. It additionally acted as a nearly complete environmental system, preventing toxins from reaching the wearer.

